---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Coming Soon — Launching Monday 16th March | Tom Pickup" description="tompickup.co.uk is being redesigned. Launching Monday 16th March 2026 with voting intelligence, council document analysis, and political accountability for Lancashire.">
  <section class="coming-soon">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="coming-soon-badge">Coming Soon</div>
      <h1 class="coming-soon-title">We&rsquo;re rebuilding<br /><span class="accent">Launching Monday 16th March</span></h1>
      <p class="coming-soon-subtitle">
        tompickup.co.uk is getting a major upgrade. Every council vote, every councillor&rsquo;s record, every decision &mdash; explained in plain English.
      </p>

      <div class="features-preview">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Voting Intelligence</h3>
          <p>See how every Lancashire councillor voted on every recorded division &mdash; with political context that actually makes sense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Council Documents</h3>
          <p>AI-analysed council minutes, officer reports, and motions &mdash; hundreds of decisions from Lancashire councils, summarised for voters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Budget Votes Decoded</h3>
          <p>No more meaningless vote counts. See exactly what was approved, how much it costs you, and who voted which way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="coming-soon-cta">
        <a href="https://aidoge.co.uk" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit AI DOGE in the meantime</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>Need to get in touch?</p>
        <div class="contact-links">
          <a href="mailto:tom@tompickup.co.uk">tom@tompickup.co.uk</a>
          <span class="divider">&bull;</span>
          <a href="https://x.com/tompickup" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@tompickup</a>
          <span class="divider">&bull;</span>
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/tompickupburnley" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="countdown-note">
        <p>Tom Pickup &bull; Lancashire County Councillor for Padiham &amp; Burnley West &bull; Reform UK</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .coming-soon {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 72px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .coming-soon-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    background: rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.25);
    color: #12B6CF;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .coming-soon-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: #f5f5f7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .accent {
    color: #12B6CF;
  }

  .coming-soon-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.7);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .features-preview {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.3);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #12B6CF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f5f5f7;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.6);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .coming-soon-cta {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #12B6CF;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #14c8e3;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-links a {
    color: #12B6CF;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-links a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .divider {
    color: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.2);
  }

  .countdown-note {
    color: rgba(245, 245, 247, 0.3);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
</style>
